    <div id="block-miller-page-title" class="miller-title-wrapper">
  
    
      
  <h1><span>February 2, 2005: State of the Union Address</span>
</h1>


    <div class="share-trigger-mobile"></div>
</div>
<div id="block-mainpagecontent">
  
    
      <article role="article" class="presidential-speech">

  
    

  <div class="ps-container video-container">
    <div class="presidential-speeches--sidebar">
      
<div  class="about-this-episode">
    <h3>About this speech</h3>
      
<div  class="about-this-episode--inner">
      
            <p class="president-name">George W. Bush</p>
      
            <p class="episode-date">February 02, 2005</p>
      
  <div class="speech-location-container">
    <span class="speech-label">Location</span>
              <span class="speech-loc">National Archives</span>
          </div>

            <div class="about-sidebar--intro"><p>In his fourth State of the Union address, President George W. Bush discusses the need to strengthen the economy, preserve the values that sustain a free democracy, and promote global peace. Bush&nbsp;focuses on the recent victories in his&nbsp;presidency and promises that the United States will adhere to its responsibilities to its people.&nbsp; He emphasizes American support for liberty at home and abroad.&nbsp;&nbsp;President Bush&nbsp;also addresses the need for Social Security reform and&nbsp;proposes new social programs.</p>
</div>
      
  </div>
  </div>
    </div>

    <div class="presidential-speeches--body-wrapper">
     <a href="/the-presidency/presidential-speeches" class="back-to-listing--cta">Presidential Speeches</a> <span class="nav-separator">|</span> <label class="presidential-speeches--label">George W. Bush Presidency</label>
      <h2 class="presidential-speeches--title"><span>February 2, 2005: State of the Union Address</span>
</h2>
      
<div  class="presidential-speeches--body">
      <div class="video-parent">
	<div class="video-container">
	<video  poster=https://millercenter.org/sites/default/files/styles/video_poster_16x9_desktop_2x/public/mc-logo-video-poster.jpg?itok=FzwnVIyd controls>
